snippet.title: Amber accepts Mikmik's friendship | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit (With Eng Subs)
snippet.description:
Amber (Krystal Mejes) shares with Divina (Pilar Pilapil) how Mikmik (Sophia Reola) saved her from the bullies in their swimming class. (With English Subtitle)
